OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774905063
OL,3,CMan who suffocated girlfriend by
OL,4,Cwrapping tape around her face jailed
OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,FA man found guilty of murdering his
OL,8,Fgirlfriend at their home in Havant by
OL,9,Fwrapping tape around her face has been
OL,10,Fjailed for life.
OL,12,FPolish national Norbert Maiksner, 49,
OL,13,Fwas found guilty of the murder of
OL,14,FFrances Obiefuleh after a trial at
OL,15,FPortsmouth Crown Court.
OL,17,FHe's been jailed for life with a
OL,18,Fminimum term of 24 years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
