PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774905063
OL,3,CMan who suffocated girlfriend by
OL,4,Cwrapping tape around her face jailed
OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,FThe court heard that a Highways
OL,8,FOfficer found Maiksner walking along
OL,9,Fthe A40 in Buckinghamshire on the
OL,10,Fmorning of April 17 2025.
OL,12,FHe told the officer that they should
OL,13,Fcall the police because he had killed
OL,14,Fhis girlfriend.
OL,16,FPaul Cavin KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,17,Fcourt said that a post-mortem
OL,18,Fexamination revealed she died of
OL,19,Fsmothering with injuries caused by
OL,20,Fcompression of the neck and chest.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
