PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774905063
OL,3,CMan who suffocated girlfriend by
OL,4,Cwrapping tape around her face jailed
OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,FHe said the defendant also had
OL,8,Fscratches to his chest and back, and
OL,9,Fadded: "The likely and frankly
OL,10,Fterrible conclusion is that they were
OL,11,Finflicted by Frances with her fingers
OL,12,Fand fingernails during the attack by
OL,13,Fthe defendant in her last moments as
OL,14,Fshe struggled to stay alive."
OL,16,FA Hampshire Police spokesman said:
OL,17,F"During his trial the court heard that
OL,18,FMaiksner had told officers that he had
OL,19,Fkilled Frances and stated that it was
OL,20,Fall a dream and that he wanted to wake
OL,21,Fup."
OL,26,@qD@HOUvD@]O]yD@AOU}D@DO]
