PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774905063
OL,3,CMan who suffocated girlfriend by
OL,4,Cwrapping tape around her face jailed
OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,FPaying tribute to Ms Obiefuleh, her
OL,8,Ffamily said in a statement released
OL,9,Fthrough police: "Frances was kind,
OL,10,Fintelligent, and resourceful ` a
OL,11,Fcaring and deeply loving mother,
OL,12,Fsister, aunt, and friend to many.
OL,14,F"She was a devoted mother and
OL,15,Fbeautiful in every sense of the word.
OL,17,F"Someone we love has been cruelly
OL,18,Ftaken from us, and it has changed our
OL,19,Flives forever.
OL,21,F"We have lost a truly beautiful soul.
OL,26,@qD@QOUvD@AOUyD@AOU}D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
