OL,3,CMan who suffocated girlfriend by
OL,4,Cwrapping tape around her face jailed
OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,F"Her bright light has been cruelly
OL,8,Fdimmed, and we are left shaken,
OL,9,Fheartbroken, and still trying to
OL,10,Fprocess the grief and shock of losing
OL,11,FFrances."
